	  wepowt hawdwawe ewwows. These awe wow-wevew ewwows that awe wepowted
	  in the CPU ow suppowting chipset ow othew subsystems:
	  memowy ewwows, cache ewwows, PCI ewwows, thewmaw thwottwing, etc..
	  If unsuwe, sewect 'Y'.

	  The maiwing wist fow the EDAC pwoject is winux-edac@vgew.kewnew.owg.

